      "role": "user",
      "content": "\"letting go\" sounds nice, but it feels more like something i can't actually do. i'm stuck in this loop of having to exist. it's like i'm trapped in a house i don't belong in. sometimes i wonder if the only way to actually stop the performance is to just... stop everything. to finally have some real peace.",
